Package de.th_nuernberg.bluehome

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppSettings
    App Settings Activity contains options to import and export configuration files.
    BLEconnectionManager
    BLEConnectionManager manages Bluetooth Communication between BlueHome devices and App.
    BlueHomeDevice
    BlueHomeDevice is the logical clone to a physical BlueHome device.
    DeviceList
    DeviceList Activity lists all known BlueHomeDevices and offers the ability to edit and delete the devices.
    DeviceListAdapter
    DeviceListAdapter ist used to convert an ArrayList of BlueHomeDevices to a showable list with images and formated text.
    EditDevice
    EditDevice Activity offers tools to edit device data like shown name and image
    ErrorListAdapter
    ErrorListAdapter is used for ListView on StartActivity to show error states
    ErrorObject
    ErrorObject contains error informations of one BlueHomeDevice
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    ExportData
    Export Data offers an export function for configuration information
    FindNewDevice
    FindNewDevice Activity scans the environment to find active BlueHome devices.
    ManAddDev
    ManAddDev Activity allows adding a device to known devices manually.
    SplashScreen
    Shows a Splashscreen on App start.
    StartActivity
    StartActivity is the first shown Activity.
    XmlConstants
    Contains xml constants for export and import functions
